<h2>Faktura za predplatne</h2>

<p>Dobry den {{owner_name}},</p>

<p>Vase faktura za predplatne <strong>{{plan_name}}</strong> za obdobi <strong>{{period}}</strong> je pripravena.</p>

<div class="details-box">
  <p><strong>Cislo faktury:</strong> {{invoice_number}}</p>
  <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 10px 0;">
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 5px 0;">Castka bez DPH:</td>
      <td style="padding: 5px 0; text-align: right;"><strong>{{formatCurrency amount currency}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 5px 0;">DPH:</td>
      <td style="padding: 5px 0; text-align: right;">{{formatCurrency vat_amount currency}}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="border-top: 2px solid #3B82F6;">
      <td style="padding: 8px 0;"><strong>Celkem:</strong></td>
      <td style="padding: 8px 0; text-align: right;"><strong>{{formatCurrency total_amount currency}}</strong></td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</div>

<p style="text-align: center;">
  <a href="{{pdf_download_url}}" class="button">Stahnout fakturu (PDF)</a>
</p>

<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 5px;">
  <a href="{{billing_portal_url}}" style="color: #3B82F6; text-decoration: underline;">Zobrazit historii faktur</a>
</p>

<p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 20px;">Tato faktura byla automaticky vystavena systemem ScheduleBox.</p>

<p>S pozdravem,<br>
Tym ScheduleBox</p>
